.NET Framework 4.0.name: SharpDox.Model.Documentation.Token
.NET Framework 4.0.description: The SharpDox.Model.Documentation.Token namespace contains all types used for the inline documentation model.

types.name: SDCodeToken
types.summary: The code token represents the "code" section of an inline documentation.

types.name: SDSeeToken
types.summary: Represents a reference within an inline documentation.

types.name: SDToken
types.summary: Represents simple text in an inline documentation and is also the base for the SDSeeToken and the SDCodeToken.
